commitResults.messageTitle: Add Level-0: Rename, Greet, and Exit
Add A-CodingStandard: Follow the Coding Standard
Add Level-4: ToDo, Event, Deadline and A-Inheritance
Rename Duke.java and edit for A-CodeQuality: Improve Code Quality
commitResults.messageBody:
Magpie.java: extract a method markTask

Marking and unmarking share some common code behaviors

Hence, new method "markTask" was created to improve code quality

runtest.bat,EXPECTED.TXT, input.txt were edited to implement
Automated Text UI testing

commitResults.messageTitle: Add classes for input and task handling and edit for error handling
commitResults.messageBody:
Created classes: inputHandler, inputValidator, and taskHandler

The switch case in Magpie.java was becoming long and inefficient

Extracting it into classes, as well as breaking it up into methods
improves readability.

Error handling was implemented in inputValidator and taskHandler

commitResults.messageTitle: Add MagpieException for A-Exceptions and edit inputValidator
commitResults.messageBody:
Validating methods in inputValidator now throws MagpieException,
which will be caught and handled to print specific error messages

commitResults.messageTitle: Sorted classes into different packages for A-Packages
Add Level-6: Delete and edit array to use ArrayList Collections
commitResults.messageBody:
Primitive data structures like a normal array are not as flexible
as java Collection classes

Hence Task Array was modified to a ArrayList data structure

deleteTask method was also added to implement Level-6

commitResults.messageTitle: Add fileHandler for Level-7: Save and edit for code quality
commitResults.messageBody:
Tasks should be saved to the hard disk when added, deleted or
changed

Hence, lets:
-Create a fileHandler class to handle file-related methods
-Create a data folder for data.txt
-Check if data.txt exists and create one if it doesn't exist
-Update file whenever task is modified by calling fileHandler
methods in taskHandler

Feedback from peers was taken into account and various method names
were edited for code quality

commitResults.messageTitle: Update fileHandler to create directory path if it does not exist
commitResults.messageBody:
Previously the path was absolute and would lead to errors

Hence fileHandler was edited to prevent errors were the path does
not exist

Minor updates were made to method names to adhere to coding
standards

commitResults.messageTitle: Refactor code to extract classes for A-MoreOOP
commitResults.messageBody:
Rename inputHandler, fileHandler, and taskHandler to Parser,
Storage, and TaskList respectively to reflect naming given in
A-MoreOOP

Extracted user interaction code into new Ui class
